- Use `pnpm install --frozen-lockfile` to ensure consistent installs across environments
- Leverage `pnpm workspaces` for monorepo management
- Utilize `pnpm patch` for quick fixes to dependencies
- Regularly run `pnpm audit` to check for security vulnerabilities
